{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2801690/extras/marketing_headings-01.png?t=1734124815\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Solaro transports you a million lightyears away, to a place without landmarks, directions, or humans of any kind... A traveller wakes up, lost and alone in space. Can you master the laws of an alien world, and guide them back toward their origins?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2801690/extras/marketing_headings-02.png?t=1734124815\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Weave your way through a vast open-world full of puzzles, trials and challenges. Master unique approaches to movement and navigation using concepts from physics and astronomy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2801690/extras/marketing_headings-03.png?t=1734124815\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Solaro is full of wild, beautiful alien environments, with their own tides, weather, atmospheres, and natural phenomena. Dive in, take a closer look, and uncover secrets buried just below the surface.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2801690/extras/marketing_headings-04.png?t=1734124815\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Designed and developed by one person over several years, Solaro features an original world with its own art, music, and design. Experience a unique artistic vision and a whole different perspective on space exploration.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2801690/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734124815","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_